snippet.textDisplay: Filmmaker Nilamadhab Panda, who hails from western Odisha and also used a remix of the song in his upcoming movie 'Kaun Kitne Paani Mein' said the MTV show promoters should have taken permission from the original composer and the lyricist. "While reproducing a masterpiece one should be very cautious about the approach and depiction not to hurt the people's sentiments. Rangabati has become an identity for western Odisha," Panda said.
snippet.textOriginal: Filmmaker Nilamadhab Panda, who hails from western Odisha and also used a remix of the song in his upcoming movie 'Kaun Kitne Paani Mein' said the MTV show promoters should have taken permission from the original composer and the lyricist.
